Package de.pcmr.shop.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AddressDoesNotBelongToUserException
    Exception is thrown if there was an attempt to change the address of a different user than the authenticated one.
    CustomerAlreadyExistsException
    Exception is thrown if a customer already exists to the given email when creating a new one.
    DuplicateOrderItemsException
    Exception is thrown if there were duplicate order items in an order entity (same article id).
    NoAddressFoundException
    Exception is thrown if no address entity was found to given ID.
    NoArticleFoundException
    Exception is thrown if no article entity was found to given ID.
    NoCustomerFoundException
    Exception is thrown if no customer entity was found to given ID.
    NotAuthorizedException
    Exception is thrown if the currently authenticated user is not authorized to perform a protected operation.
    NotEnoughArticlesOnStockException
    Exception is thrown if there are not enough articles on stock for a given order.
    PasswordException
    Exception is thrown if there was any exception during change of credentials.
    UploadedImageInvalidFileExtensionException
    Exception is thrown if an uploaded image file has an invalid file extension.
    UploadedImageResolutionTooLowException
    Exception is thrown if an uploaded image file has a too low resolution.
